sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Svelte)
    participant A as App (Wails Binding)
    participant PM as PlanningManager
    participant PA as PlanAccess
    participant R as Repository (Git)

    Note over C,R: GetYearFocus
    C->>A: GetYearFocus(year)
    A->>PM: GetYearFocus(year)
    PM->>PM: Validate year 1900-9999
    PM->>PA: GetYearFocus(year)
    PA->>PA: ReadFile(calendar/{year}.json)
    PA-->>PM: []DayFocus
    PM-->>A: []DayFocus
    A->>A: Convert to Wails DTOs
    A-->>C: []DayFocus (Wails DTO)

    Note over C,R: SaveDayFocus
    C->>A: SaveDayFocus(day)
    A->>PM: SaveDayFocus(access.DayFocus)
    PM->>PM: Validate date non-empty
    PM->>PA: SaveDayFocus(day)
    PA->>PA: extractYearFromDate()
    PA->>PA: GetYearFocus(year) [read existing]
    PA->>PA: Upsert entry, sort by date
    PA->>PA: WriteJSON(calendar/{year}.json)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PA-->>PM: nil
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: ClearDayFocus
    C->>A: ClearDayFocus(date)
    A->>PM: ClearDayFocus(date)
    PM->>PA: GetDayFocus(date)
    PA->>PA: GetYearFocus() -> find by date
    PA-->>PM: *DayFocus (or nil)
    alt Entry exists
        PM->>PA: SaveDayFocus({date, nil themeIDs, preserve notes/text})
        PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    end
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil
